Packages that use net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict.query
net.ajaest.jdk.core.main contains JavaDIKt's main classes (Launcher, Messages, GUIEngine,...) 
net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict contains specific JavaDiKt's database management classes. 
net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict.auxi contains specific JavaDiKt's auxiliary classes for database API 
net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict.query contains specific JavaDiKt's auxiliary classes for query API 
net.ajaest.jdk.data.dict.query.kanjiFields contains specific JavaDiKt's auxiliary classes for data API
